name: Globe Caterer
description: When it comes to driving the resources to the world Farmer is the one which is giving real-life saver of world. The food we have on the plate was grown on the farms with lots of hard work which we consider granted. Globe Caterer is an artwork dedicated to farmers of the world. When it comes to the life cycle major role is played in every era is by farmers. This artwork show farmer as a mother how feeds baby as responsibility and love. The sky is indigo blue to show the history of farming. The leaf shown in the work is representing farms and the wild life of farmers.
